title: Mocallure 12-Color Lip Palette / Long-Lasting Professional Lip Kit For Every Mood
description:
TheMocallure 12-Color Lip Paletteis a versatile and budget-friendly makeup essential, perfect for those who love experimenting with different lip looks. This palette offers a range of shades suitable for various occasions, from everyday wear to special events.

? Product Highlights
12 Vibrant Shades: The palette includes a mix of matte and shiny finishes, allowing you to create diverse lip looks.Long-Lasting Formula: Designed to stay in place throughout the day without fading or smudging.Moisturizing Ingredients: Infused with Moringa Oil, Raspberry Seed Oil, and Vitamin E to nourish and hydrate your lips.Portable Design: Compact and lightweight, making it ideal for travel and on-the-go touch-ups.Shades: Pink , Red , Mahron , PeachSize ; 2.5g
